## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack  
- **Language:** Python  
- **Framework:** PyTorch  
- **Model:** YOLOv5 (custom-trained)  
- **Dataset:** [Roboflow Baby Detection Dataset](https://universe.roboflow.com/vtar/baby-object-detection-final)  
